---
title: Easy As Smokey Crumbed Pork Salad with Avocado & Herby Mayonnaise
description: Schnitzel and salad? Yes please! Let’s cook up some golden crumbed pork and serve it on a bed of crisp mixed leaves, pan-fried capsicum and creamy avo. Drizzle on the herby mayo for a fresh twist that’ll make your taste buds dance. Smokey, zesty, and downright delicious - dig in!
